title: "Qualcomm stock pops on Apple supply deal"
text: "Shares of Qualcomm (QCOM) jumped on the news that it will provide Apple (AAPL) with 5G chips for the iPhone through 2026. It could be a sign that Apple isn't quite ready to start going it alone on chips quite yet."

title: "Apple's Chip Struggles Add Time to Qualcomm's Clock"
text: "Keeping an iPhone business deal for a couple more years will help the chip maker's diversification plan."
